// Stage 3 换心 retirement regression: this explicit hand-written body is the
// LEGACY two-scope Gearbox dequant form (gearbox_cross_region_handoff carrier +
// vsetvl_region_markers + a nested consumer tcrv_rvv.with_vl scope). The
// low-precision product-reduction dequant body now lowers ONLY through the real
// RVV->emitc DialectConversion, which owns the single-scope no-handoff body; the
// legacy statement-plan dequant emission is retired (fail-closed, I7). So this
// two-scope dequant body no longer has a legal route: the convert-gate refuses the
// handoff form and the legacy path errors with a bounded diagnostic instead of
// synthesizing C. The positive PLAN/HEADER artifact coverage for this op kind now
// lives on the single-scope pre-realized fixture
// (pre-realized-selected-body-artifact-widening-product-reduce-dequantize-f32.mlir).
